Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.35,Main - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,ما هذا؟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:17:57.45,Main - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,ما هذا؟
